txt.en: 'The tower is ours! Those Free People will take it back unless we act. Get out into the wilds and get what we need to build a door to seal off the top of the tower. Then we can slaughter the Free Folk at our own pace.'
Deliver the materials to Gozad at Tiríth Rhaw
'Impressive, maggot. It looks as though you really want to advance in our army. Good work. Don't rest though, the Free People will return.'
It has been strongly recommended that you acquire materials needed to build a gate that will defend the interior of Tiriíth Rhaw.
'Go get the materials we need! We need to defend this tower.'
Make your way into the wilds of the Ettenmoors and collect the materials needed to construct the internal gate.
